We recommended, and the Local Chief Executive agreed to direct the:
the MDRRMO to utilize the LDRRMF in accordance with the approved LDRRMFIP;
the Municipal Budget Officer to:
support any changes in the LDRRMFIP with augmentation, re-alignment, supplemental budget, or ordinances, if any;
be vigilant in the charging of disbursements to avoid illegal utilization of funds;
the Municipal Accountant to:
utilize the LDRRMF in accordance with the approved LDRRMFIP;
prepare the necessary adjusting entries;
the Municipal Treasurer to:
cause the complete transfer of the amount disbursed in General Fund to the LDRRMF – Special Trust Fund account; and
be cautious in issuing checks to avoid unlawful transfer and utilization of funds.

